data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This turnkey three-bedroom, two-bathroom residence is move in ready for it's new homeowners! Nestled in a prime location, this gem boasts an updated and spacious floor plan that's perfect for both relaxation and entertainment.    Indulge in the convenience of being just minutes away from the magic of Disneyland, ensuring endless fun and enjoyment for you and your loved ones. The vibrant neighborhood also offers easy access to a plethora of entertainment options and shopping destinations, providing the ideal blend of leisure and convenience.    With a single-car garage and a dedicated parking spot, you'll never have to worry about finding a place to park. Imagine the ease of coming home and effortlessly parking your vehicle in your private garage or designated spot.    Step outside to your own private patio, the perfect space for al fresco dining, morning coffee, or simply unwinding after a long day. Additionally, enjoy the luxury of a nearby community pool, offering a refreshing retreat just steps from your front door.
